title: Differential cross-section for inelastic scattering of 14-MeV neutrons by niobium

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Atomic Energy, Vol.58, p.152 (1985)
Prog: Fiz.-Energ Institut, Obninsk Reports, No.1406 (1983)

x4freetext: Differential cross-section for inelastic scattering of
Flight base 2.4 m and 7.m, resolution 1.3 and
Hollow cylinders of 45 mm long, 45mm outside diameter,
outside diameter 35mm for 2.4m base, 15mm for 7m base.
Efficiency was determined by Cf-252 SF neutron spectra
Each of 3 normalizations had accuracy ~5%,all 3 results
For multiple scattering calculated by Monte Carlo
Total error - root of squared errors .
correction for neutron beam attenuation and
Data are on Fig.1 of SJA,58,152,1985
